coroutine = asynchronous

Our MVVM of auth :

├── java
│   ├── com.munchbot.munchbot (Main package)
│   │   ├── ui
│   │   │   ├── auth (New package for authentication views)
│   │   │   │   ├── LoginActivity.kt (New Activity for login)
│   │   │   │   ├── SignUpActivity.kt (New Activity for sign-up)
│   │   │   │   └── AuthViewModel.kt (New ViewModel to handle authentication logic)
│   │   ├── data
│   │   │   ├── model
│   │   │   │   └── com.munchbot.munchbot.User.kt (New data class for com.munchbot.munchbot.User)
│   │   │   ├── repository
│   │   │   │   └── SignUpDataRepository.kt (New Repository for user data)
│   │   │   └── remote
│   │   │       └── FirebaseDataSource.kt (New Data Source for Firebase operations)
│   │   └── utils
│   │       └── Resource.kt (New utility class for handling data state)
└───└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


